+Compatibility matrix:
+
+| Formula source | Old binary that only knows `contract` | New binary with `formula_v2 = false` | New binary with `formula_v2 = true` |
+|---|---|---|---|
+| No requirement and no v2-only constructs | Works | Works | Works |
